// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - MM_Rogue_SL8-9_Task_02 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1522029109" "Some may think it's not right to steal the hard-earned work of others. However, you like to see it as taking payment from those who would otherwise <i>not</i> pay you for saving their lives. After all, this is what's <i>best</i> for everyone, isn't it? Especially if you consider that you're fighting Malta. Nobody enjoys going up against those guys, so it's all the better that you deserve some payment for this!"
// AcceptString :
"P1332526885" "Save the day and take your payment!"
// SendOffString :
"P130189811" "You'll have to somehow make your way to Striga Isle, then strike at Malta while there's still time left!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2689498253" "Stop Malta and Steal your Payment!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3873162050" "You'll have to hurry, otherwise the goods you're after may be long gone! Not to mention those people you're supposed to rescue."
// TaskTitle :
"P1813490322" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>One Rogue's Work, Another Rogue's Pay</color></span></scale></font>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3088266797" "You arrive in Striga Isle to see Malta has indeed taken over this entire part of the island. You'll have to find your payment first before making any moves to save those supers."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3936830542" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>One Rogue's Work, Another Rogue's Pay</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Morality Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Now that the situation is settled, you're able to look at all the loot you acquired, and it is all <i>very</i> good. Silent Blade stole a number of magical artifacts, Savage Siren had several bits of expensive technology, and Stardusk had several dufflebags filled with money! All in a day's work for you. Maybe you should look into rescuing these three more often!"

